{"tid":1680080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實黑警已經拎緊政府其他部門既錢用","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:18:59.000Z","uid":58168,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5ea4a92b872ec9514dfdf23eabf30cb97ecf77","tid":1680080,"uid":58168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"政府營地本身定期都有筆錢收用黎經營，但係最近cut左一大筆資源，人都炒左一大班，目的就係資助班狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢見到，冇fc，只係見到呢兩日都有人開post講班狗既人工資源問題，所以同大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd59536bc180a3ab7272bfd792edde2aa81ca29","tid":1680080,"uid":58168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"推比人見到"},{"pid":"bbb91b4efe429bd6fa42e511e8f0c9d3f198d45c","tid":1680080,"uid":58168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都有負評係咩事"},{"pid":"2fdebef47a93f23cd632ad2d8efa798fb77cde1b","tid":1680080,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a75ef2b71b9b04b18076925ad6c5d24f57284715","tid":1680080,"uid":58168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fdebef47a93f23cd632ad2d8efa798fb77cde1b","tid":1680080,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb91b4efe429bd6fa42e511e8f0c9d3f198d45c","tid":1680080,"uid":58168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都有負評係咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"推到有同行出聲"},{"pid":"b308b3a34c97a6a66fc00f9701e8b420806cd46e","tid":1680080,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"唔好理真唔真<br />\n總之繼續企出黎遊行示威<br />\n打擊曬個經濟<br />\n亦都令政府洗費大幅增加<br />\n咁先係真正既攬炒<br />\n愈近攬炒就愈比到政府壓力去回應訴求<br />\n而家一係市民被打壓到驚唔再企出黎<br />\n一係就經濟仆直令到政府要讓步<br />\n唔係